news.title: Kolkata metro's Purple Line to be completed by 2028-29
news.para: Officials said the tunnel-boring machines (TBMs), manufactured by Germany's Herrenknecht and being assembled in Chennai, will start arriving in Dec.

news.title: DMRC seeks 7,200 crore in Delhi budget to 'fulfil commitments'
news.para: In a letter to the chief secretary, DMRC managing director Vikas Kumar said if the funds were not made available timely, the execution of phase-IV would be delayed, leading to cost overrun.

news.title: Deep Financial Consultants' director buys flat in Mumbai for over Rs 105 crore
news.para: The apartment spread over a total of over 7,139 sq ft area in one of the wings of the tower Oberoi Three Sixty West on Dr Annie Besant Road is on the 59th floor and 43rd habitable floor.

news.title: Pomburpa land conversion faces PIL challenge in Bombay HC
news.para: Architect Dean D’Cruz has challenged the conversion sanad, technical clearance, building licence, and the conversion.

news.title: After two-year ban, residents get nod to repair damaged homes in Jyotirmath
news.para: District magistrate Sandeep Tiwari issued the order "in public interest, granting permission for temporary repairs to residential buildings" in response to mounting demands from the affected residents to let them rebuild their homes ahead of the winter season.

news.title: Conviction of Brajesh Construction's directors upheld over non-payment of TDS
news.para: A magistrate court had convicted Brajesh Construction Pvt Ltd, along with its directors, Premal Parekh and Neha Parekh to three months imprisonment and imposed a fine of Rs 5,000.

news.title: Fresh period of limitation to run on continuous breach of contract: NCDRC
news.para: The National Commission observed that continuing wrong occurs when a party continuously breaches an obligation imposed by law or agreement.

news.title: Akzo Nobel India to monetize non-productive immovable properties
news.para: Anil Chaudhry has been appointed on the board of directors of Akzo Nobel India as an additional director in the category of an independent director with effect from November 22, 2024 for a period of three years.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh cabinet approves Noida-Greater Noida metro extension
news.para: UP finance minister Suresh Khanna said the extension would be 17.435 km long. The central and state govts will spend Rs 394 crore each on the project.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC names defaulters who owe Rs 222 crore property tax
news.para: According to a civic release, seizure notices were issued under Section 203 of the MMC Act to defaulters who delayed paying property tax within the prescribed period, despite having the financial capacity to pay.

news.title: Hyderabad development body implements 10-day deadline for building permission
news.para: HMDA metropolitan commissioner Sarfaraz Ahmad on Thursday said a special drive was undertaken to reduce pending applications within HMDA beyond 30 days to zero from the last week of Oct.

news.title: Nine landlords booked in J&K's Samba for not providing tenant details
news.para: "Police have registered nine FIRs against house and land owners in Samba for not providing details of tenants during a verification drive launched across the district," a police spokesman said.

news.title: Mahindra Lifespaces & Sumitomo Corporation's JV to invest Rs 225 crore to expand Tamil Nadu's industrial park
news.para: The joint venture partners i.e. shareholders of Mahindra Industrial Park Chennai will invest approximately Rs 225 crore towards development of the project.

news.title: London-focused Workspace resizes units as demand rises for smaller offices
news.para: Unlike larger office landlords in the UK, Workspace offers unfurnished spaces on relatively short-term leases to mostly small- and medium-sized enterprises and entrepreneurs - from architects and florists to podcasters and app developers.

news.title: Average gross rental yield touch 3.62% in 13 Indian cities: Report
news.para: Ahmedabad tops the list with a rental yield of 3.9%. The city’s average monthly rent has increased by 16.9% year-on-year to Rs 19.35 per sq ft, while property prices average Rs 5,927 per sq ft.

news.title: Calcutta HC stays demolition of illegal constructions in Mandarmoni
news.para: Passing the interim stay on demolition of the alleged illegal constructions near the sea beach at Mandarmoni on the Bay of Bengal coast, Justice Amrita Sinha directed that the notice of November 11 will not be given effect to till December 13 or until further order, whichever is earlier.

news.title: Institutional real estate investments in India to grow further in 2025: Report
news.para: In the first three quarters of 2024 alone, investments have reached USD 4.7 billion, accounting for 87% of the inflows in the entire year of 2023. This momentum also sets a promising tone for institutional investments across real estate asset classes in 2025.

news.title: Indore: Drone survey to clear encroachments near Kanh and Saraswati rivers
news.para: Based on its survey conducted around five months ago, IMC had identified encroachments within 30 metres of HFL of both the rivers. The civic body has planned phase-wise removal of all structures falling within the set limit of the water bodies.

news.title: ACC and Ambuja Cements trade over 2% higher post Adani's US indictments
news.para: Adani Green Energy dropped 10.95 per cent and Adani Energy Solutions tumbled 8.57 per cent to hit the 52-week low of Rs 637.85 on the BSE.

news.title: NCR: CAQM issues directive to expedite action against pollution norm violators under GRAP
news.para: CAQM held the 18th meeting of its Sub-Committee on Safeguarding and Enforcement on Wednesday to monitor and review sector-specific enforcement actions by NCR state governments, the Government of the National Capital Territory of Delhi (GNCTD), and Punjab.
